sendSmsChallenge(Client, String, Factor) - Static method in class okta.unit.testing.OktaFunctions
This function is used to send sms with OTP to the user when login credentials are successfully authenticated when multifator authentication is required for login by taking stateToken as input from the function authenticateUser().
sendSmsFactor(Client, User, Factor) - Static method in class okta.unit.testing.OktaFunctions
This function is used to send sms to the user with passcode(OTP).
